title: How we’re using dogs to sniff out malaria | James Logan | TEDxLondon

media:group.media:title: How we’re using dogs to sniff out malaria | James Logan | TEDxLondon
media:group.media:description:
James Logan explores how dogs can potentially detect and save lives from malaria. This talk was filmed at TEDxLondon. 

Watch the full talk here: https://youtu.be/n05PJKGtM8I

Start each day with short, eye-opening ideas from some of the world’s greatest TEDx speakers.
